      "writtenOn": "2019-05-23T22:55:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Maybe mention that shard is a function only of key, not tile, so that a given key is on the same shard across all tiles.\n\nAlternatively, rename \"key\" to \"subkey\" to avoid confusion with \"row key\".\n\n(BTW, is there any particular reason that a given key should be on the same shard across tiles? It\u0027s mentioned in the doc for DefaultShards in bt_tracestore/types.go, but I can\u0027t think of a reason that\u0027s necessary or even desirable.)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 85,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 85,
        "endChar": 71
