      "writtenOn": "2019-05-25T14:41:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Done, with rename to subkey.\n\nSpeculation as to why follows:\n\nThis is more a factor with perf, which fetches across many tiles, but having the same trace on the same shard means that they will be closer alphabetically. BT says that related entities should be on rows that adjacent (maybe that also means nearby rows?)",
